Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:40.62,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌声の止む時は　運命の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:48.50,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}そうとだけ決めていた　故は分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:56.47,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}金色も褪せるほど　焦がれてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:03.65,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憧れの輪郭は　遠ざかってくみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:10.99,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溢れるよ　ほら手のひら　握り返してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:15.45,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}痛みと痛みとりがえよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:19.20,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}糧にするんだ　落花の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.91,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}全て傷ついて僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:27.29,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}かたどってく　かたちになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:32.84,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}目覚めの先で　往こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.26,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}ずっと　響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:40.62,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌声止息之时  就是命运的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:48.50,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}我只知这样的结论  却不知其原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:56.47,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的渴望之情能使黄金褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:03.65,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而憧憬的轮廓  却似乎渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:10.99,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我思绪漫溢  快来握紧我的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:15.45,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}用苦痛来交换苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:19.20,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}用落花残片充当食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.91,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}我用所有创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:27.29,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}模仿着塑造自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:32.84,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}向着觉醒的前方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.26,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}让歌声永远传唱
Comment: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ending-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.35,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still remember you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.81,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The time we shared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.39,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The love you gave
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.36,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Though everything has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.07,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You push me to live on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:29.91,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海よりも深い奥底から見守っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:35.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かれた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:43.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still love you, even though I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:52.06,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永久に続く悲しみの夜の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:56.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:02.57,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will be here for you, always and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:08.83,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もずっと願っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:19.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温かいこの闇の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得我们共度的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.39,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得你给予我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管一切都已面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.07,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仍是我活着的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:29.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自比海更深的幽穴深底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:35.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守护着各自分歧的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:43.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然爱着你  即使我只能思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:52.06,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在通向永恒的哀恸深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:56.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犹自有爱存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:02.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会为你守在这里  始终如一  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:08.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我仍将继续为你祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:19.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这温暖的黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sign-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:16.89,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.93,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小孩子很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.00,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雕刻她使我极其过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.21,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有幸装饰这枚乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.25,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}带给我绝顶的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.17,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去吧  人类孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.01,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要你与石头同在  价值就会延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.42,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家一起上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.46,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.20,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.18,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.32,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}铁线队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.61,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压住它！
